	.string "Kira: Oh?\n"
	.string "We were searching for treasures.\l"
	.string "But we discovered a Trainer instead!$"

AbandonedShip_Rooms2_1F_Text_KiraDefeat:
	.string "Kira: Ooh, so strong!$"

AbandonedShip_Rooms2_1F_Text_KiraPostBattle:
